Carter-Day INdustries Inc saidit reached an eight mln dlrs settlement in a suit filed in theBankruptcy Court for the Southern District of N.Y. against fivepower companies.    The suit was filed against Montana Power Co &lt;MTP>, PugetSound Power and Light Co &lt;PSD>, Portland General Electric Co&lt;PGN>, Washington Water Power Co &lt;WWP> and PacifiCorp's &lt;PPW>Pacific Power and Light Co.    Carter-Day said proceeds from the settlement will be usedto restore the company's liquidity, working capital and networth. Reuter&#3;